00:00:02.800 --> 00:00:08.400
All right. First I would like to tell you about

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:14.960
the meaning of puja.

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.440
There are two aspects.

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.560
One is the aspect

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:40.080
that you have got your own

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:45.040
deities within yourself.

00:00:58.840 --> 00:01:02.720
And these deities are to be awakened within you.

00:01:08.080 --> 00:01:12.400
Deities are the different aspects of one God.

00:01:27.480 --> 00:01:30.160
So on one side you have the Deities,

00:01:30.360 --> 00:01:32.280
means the aspects of God,

00:01:32.480 --> 00:01:34.960
which are all the time awakened.

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:40.200
On the other side you have your own Deities,

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:44.840
which are sometimes awakened, sometimes half-awakened,

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:48.840
sometimes sleeping and sometimes sick.

00:02:31.960 --> 00:02:37.720
So you have to use two methods:

00:02:38.160 --> 00:02:42.680
one to please the Deities

00:02:42.880 --> 00:02:45.200
of God,

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:49.560
and to ask them to bless your Deities,

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:55.520
or to ask them to awaken your Deities.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:30.920
So by doing the puja, means when you offer anything

00:03:31.120 --> 00:03:34.000
that you have got to offer,

00:03:34.200 --> 00:03:38.480
anything that you offer is - say, flowers,

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:41.720
if you want to offer flower to God,

00:03:41.920 --> 00:03:43.400
you don't have to speak anything,

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:46.560
you have to just offer, that "this is for You."

00:03:46.760 --> 00:03:49.880
Anybody can understand offering,

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:52.760
for that you don't have to have even a tongue.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:56.440
Even if a blind man is there, if he wants to give you something,

00:03:56.640 --> 00:03:58.480
he can just give you like this.

00:03:58.680 --> 00:04:00.960
And that expression is sufficient

00:04:01.160 --> 00:04:03.640
for anybody to be convinced that he can offer it.

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:07.160
You don't have to say anything about it.

00:04:23.160 --> 00:04:27.360
So now, when you offer a flower to God,

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:30.840
even if you don't say a mantra

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:35.080
it is offered - all right, it's given.

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:40.160
But whether it is accepted or not is a problem.

00:05:23.280 --> 00:05:27.600
But now, when you are a realized soul and you offer anything,

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:32.080
it is acceptable to God even if you don't say anything.

00:05:56.800 --> 00:06:02.040
But what about you getting any reward out of it?

00:06:14.960 --> 00:06:20.080
After realization when you offer anything to God, He accepts,

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:24.440
because it's coming from a realized soul, so He accepts.

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:29.760
Now, how do we get

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:35.480
blessed by Him, by giving a flower to God?

00:07:03.240 --> 00:07:05.480
Now if you don't say anything about it,

00:07:05.680 --> 00:07:08.040
you just offer a flower,

00:07:08.240 --> 00:07:12.280
then you might be rewarded with many flowers

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:15.920
automatically in life.

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:42.720
Or you may be, whatever material things you offer,

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:45.560
you may be blessed materially.

00:08:02.880 --> 00:08:07.240
Then in a subtler way if you say something,

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:10.160
as you say for offering somebody

00:08:10.360 --> 00:08:13.040
that humble way of saying that

00:08:13.240 --> 00:08:16.720
"I'll be happy if You would accept this,"

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:21.880
will be even subtler results of that maybe,

00:08:22.320 --> 00:08:27.600
which could be much wider, maybe much deeper.

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:11.200
Now, you do something symbolic

00:09:11.400 --> 00:09:15.080
which is very, the essence, the principle of something.

00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:17.840
Like flowers are the -

00:09:18.040 --> 00:09:21.480
they represent the principle of the Mother Earth.

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.600
Now,

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:48.640
so the symbolicism of all the things

00:09:48.840 --> 00:09:52.720
that we can offer to God has been meditated upon,

00:09:52.920 --> 00:09:55.280
and has been found out.

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:26.600
So they use five things called as panchamruta,

00:10:26.800 --> 00:10:28.960
as we have here.

00:10:43.680 --> 00:10:46.040
Because if you have hit the principle,

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:49.320
then you have really hit the whole, isn't it.

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:06.280
Because spiritual well-being is a total well-being.

00:11:06.480 --> 00:11:09.080
It's not just partly that your material well-being

00:11:09.280 --> 00:11:12.200
or your physical well-being, or your emotional well-being,

00:11:12.400 --> 00:11:13.840
or your mental well-being.

00:11:14.040 --> 00:11:18.480
It's a total one, completely balanced into totality.

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:55.640
Now when you offer these other things like the,

00:12:01.280 --> 00:12:03.480
we call them akshadas,

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:10.960
what do you call ?

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:16.160
Turmeric. Turmeric rice, you see, this yellow thing, you see.

00:12:16.400 --> 00:12:18.600
When you offer this, you know, the yellow color

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:21.440
is that of the Swadisthana Chakra.

00:12:21.640 --> 00:12:25.160
And rice is very dear to all the gods.

00:12:53.280 --> 00:12:56.680
Now there's a trick in it, because it's a human trick.

00:12:56.880 --> 00:12:59.040
Gods are fond of rice.

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:01.120
So they put turmeric on it,

00:13:01.320 --> 00:13:05.640
means that "We offer to You a rice which is yellow-colored"

00:13:05.840 --> 00:13:11.720
- means, "You should give us blessings of our creativity."

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:14.600
When you eat it, more creativity will flow

00:13:14.800 --> 00:13:18.040
and we'll be blessed by that deity - it's a trick.

00:14:04.960 --> 00:14:09.480
The whole thing of puja is the trick of human saints, you see,

00:14:09.680 --> 00:14:13.800
how to trick God to give more blessings!

00:14:36.960 --> 00:14:41.080
But whatever God likes, it has to be auspicious and holy.

00:14:41.280 --> 00:14:43.760
So ultimately it works out for the

00:14:43.960 --> 00:14:49.000
holiness of saints and their simple hearts.

00:15:20.880 --> 00:15:25.520
Now, the puja cannot be done by a person who is not a realized soul.

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:34.560
A person who preaches also has to be a realized soul,

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:37.760
the one who does Namaz has to be a realized soul,

00:15:37.960 --> 00:15:41.960
the one who prays has to be a realized soul.

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:31.440
So all the utensils that are used are to be worshipped in a way

00:16:31.640 --> 00:16:34.800
that they are to be holy things,

00:16:35.000 --> 00:16:36.720
they are to be respected things.

00:16:36.920 --> 00:16:40.400
You cannot use anything, say the one you are using in the bathroom

00:16:40.600 --> 00:16:44.160
and you use the same thing for the puja, is absurd.

00:17:18.720 --> 00:17:20.400
Three things are very important,

00:17:20.600 --> 00:17:23.560
is a ghatah, means [water pot] the vessel,

00:17:23.920 --> 00:17:26.480
vessel that contains the kundalini,

00:17:26.680 --> 00:17:29.000
the vessel that contains the

00:17:29.960 --> 00:17:33.960
primordial desire within us to get to God,

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:36.600
is first to be worshipped, our desire.

00:17:36.800 --> 00:17:39.400
Is the ghatah, is the one made here.

00:17:39.600 --> 00:17:42.400
And on top is called as a Shriphala.

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:46.120
Shriphala means this also has got water in it, if you  see,

00:17:46.320 --> 00:17:52.160
the coconut represents the same thing.

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:52.720
Now in the subtler form it is

00:18:52.920 --> 00:18:58.560
the water of all the rivers of the world.

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:13.960
And the coconut is the water of all the oceans.

00:19:39.440 --> 00:19:42.480
The water from the ocean or sea

00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:47.000
rises through the tree-trunk of the coconut,

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:51.520
and becomes the sweet water in the coconut.

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:54.400
It's a symbolic thing.

00:20:28.560 --> 00:20:33.040
So this is the vessel called ghatah-puja, this is the ghatah-puja.

00:20:34.320 --> 00:20:36.320
Now, I don't want to go to details today,

00:20:36.520 --> 00:20:38.240
because we have to talk about Ganesha.

00:20:38.440 --> 00:20:41.840
The same is - now that is water, all right.

00:20:42.040 --> 00:20:47.360
Then we have to worship Ghanta (bell) and Shankha (shell).

00:20:47.560 --> 00:20:52.240
These are two representing the sound.

00:21:02.320 --> 00:21:03.360
Shell.

00:21:25.560 --> 00:21:30.120
Actually the Shankha represents the ether.

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:43.120
Then we have the Deepa, means what?

00:21:43.320 --> 00:21:49.160
It's the light, represents the light element, called as tejas.

00:22:01.120 --> 00:22:05.880
Normally also to the Goddess they also give Her a fan,

00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:09.880
which represents the air element.

00:22:29.080 --> 00:22:32.360
So this is how all the five elements

00:22:32.560 --> 00:22:37.080
are pleased beforehand, using them.

00:22:37.280 --> 00:22:42.040
So the essences of these or the causal essences

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:44.960
of these five elements

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:47.920
should be pleased at this time,

00:22:48.440 --> 00:22:52.000
should be supporting the puja.

00:23:12.240 --> 00:23:15.320
Now there are also all kinds of other things,

00:23:15.520 --> 00:23:20.280
like your family deities, you might be

00:23:20.480 --> 00:23:22.640
worshipping in your family some deities.

00:23:22.840 --> 00:23:26.360
They should not be also at this time upsetting the puja;

00:23:26.560 --> 00:23:29.480
or maybe the forefathers who are dead.

00:23:29.680 --> 00:23:31.840
All these things are to be quietened,

00:23:32.040 --> 00:23:35.120
so that they should be told that this is a puja like this,

00:23:35.320 --> 00:23:37.560
and you do not disturb us at this time.

00:23:37.760 --> 00:23:39.720
Means even thoughts should not come,

00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:42.160
their thoughts or their - any disturbances.

00:23:42.360 --> 00:23:46.160
So everything is to be first made into peace.

00:24:06.400 --> 00:24:09.160
Now this is the one aspect I have told you in short,

00:24:09.360 --> 00:24:12.080
because it's a very long thing. If I have to speak about it

00:24:12.280 --> 00:24:14.480
I'll have to speak at least three times,

00:24:14.680 --> 00:24:19.920
and with three hours each time, still it may not be finished.

00:25:06.640 --> 00:25:08.760
Now we come to the second aspect,

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:11.160
which question I asked you "What do you,

00:25:11.360 --> 00:25:14.480
how do you get benefited by it?"

00:25:40.320 --> 00:25:45.760
So apart from this technique, to have the best

00:25:47.960 --> 00:25:49.920
effect of the blessings

00:25:50.120 --> 00:25:55.960
or the best flow of the Grace within us,

00:25:56.280 --> 00:25:58.800
we say mantras.

00:26:14.600 --> 00:26:17.320
The sound of mantras,

00:26:22.040 --> 00:26:25.760
the sound, the sound echo

00:26:25.960 --> 00:26:30.120
into the being of God.

00:26:41.640 --> 00:26:45.520
And they are re-echoed on our chakras,

00:26:52.400 --> 00:26:55.800
and then the chakras start opening more.

00:27:00.200 --> 00:27:04.680
So the flow of the Grace of God is received.

00:27:16.440 --> 00:27:20.240
But only a realized soul should chant a mantra.

00:27:27.720 --> 00:27:31.960
Because without connection, how will it reach God?

00:27:41.600 --> 00:27:43.400
It is a vicious circle.

00:27:46.760 --> 00:27:50.280
Now one may say that "Mother, you cannot get realization

00:27:50.480 --> 00:27:53.120
unless and until you get the Grace of God.

00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:12.400
And the chakras won't open by a person

00:28:12.600 --> 00:28:14.480
who is not a realized soul.

00:28:24.160 --> 00:28:27.200
And without opening the chakras you cannot get realization."

00:28:34.880 --> 00:28:39.640
That's how the play of the Mother comes in,

00:28:43.680 --> 00:28:46.600
and of all the saints, like you.

00:28:56.800 --> 00:29:02.400
I would say the Sahaja yogis have to break this vicious circle.

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:16.520
You have to raise the kundalini yourself.

00:29:22.920 --> 00:29:25.760
Once you raise the kundalini, the kundalini opens

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:27.880
the chakras a little bit,

00:29:36.840 --> 00:29:40.800
because you have given your vibrations to the chakras.

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:51.080
So once she knows there is a Sahaja yogi standing

00:29:51.280 --> 00:29:54.760
behind the seeker, she rises.

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:16.960
She knows you are her brothers and sisters,

00:30:22.680 --> 00:30:26.120
and that you belong to the same family as she does.

00:30:41.200 --> 00:30:43.840
She knows the land where she has to grow, you see,

00:30:44.040 --> 00:30:48.320
so she can feel that, and then she rises in her dignity.

00:31:00.400 --> 00:31:03.080
That's how she breaks this vicious circle.

00:31:10.320 --> 00:31:15.400
That's why in the beginning we don't tell them about the mantras,

00:31:20.920 --> 00:31:26.120
because in the mantras you have to accept Me as the Deity.

00:31:43.920 --> 00:31:48.400
In this advent of Mine it is made compulsory

00:31:48.600 --> 00:31:51.760
that you have to recognize Me.

00:32:06.080 --> 00:32:08.520
Because this is very precarious,

00:32:08.720 --> 00:32:10.760
the Resurrection Time we can call it,

00:32:10.960 --> 00:32:14.160
or the time of your Last Judgment.

00:32:25.920 --> 00:32:28.320
First the realization has to be given

00:32:28.520 --> 00:32:31.600
without any recognition.

00:32:44.680 --> 00:32:49.360
But not to those who are denying or insulting Me.

00:32:58.120 --> 00:33:00.800
Under any circumstances they cannot get realization,

00:33:01.000 --> 00:33:03.320
whatever you may try.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:19.280
Even after realization if people start thinking against Me,

00:33:19.480 --> 00:33:21.320
vibrations will stop,

00:33:35.240 --> 00:33:36.960
because of Sahasrara.

00:33:38.560 --> 00:33:41.960
And the heart has to be

00:33:42.200 --> 00:33:45.720
completely in unison with Me,

00:33:45.920 --> 00:33:49.880
otherwise Sahasrara is closed.

00:34:15.560 --> 00:34:19.680
Now those people who are simple,

00:34:19.880 --> 00:34:24.320
who are full of open heart, you see,

00:34:24.520 --> 00:34:27.520
such people understand Me very well and

00:34:27.720 --> 00:34:30.960
they just put Me in their hearts.

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:49.360
After realization,

00:34:49.560 --> 00:34:53.680
after going through the understanding of Sahaja Yoga,

00:34:53.880 --> 00:34:58.960
through their mental activity, also the intellectuals understand Me

00:34:59.200 --> 00:35:04.160
and recognize Me in a little circuitous way.

00:35:41.800 --> 00:35:46.280
After the puja, when they receive the blessings,

00:35:46.480 --> 00:35:49.640
a very blissful state they achieve,

00:35:49.840 --> 00:35:55.560
then they realize the value of puja also - afterwards.

00:36:23.440 --> 00:36:24.640
Now in India,

00:36:24.840 --> 00:36:27.800
where the puja system has been traditionally coming

00:36:28.000 --> 00:36:30.280
and has been maintained quite a lot,

00:36:30.480 --> 00:36:34.560
they understand it without any mental processes.

00:36:52.960 --> 00:36:55.720
But when they meet somebody, an intellectual,

00:36:55.960 --> 00:36:58.640
who has become a Sahaja yogi, you see

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:02.240
they can't understand them.

00:37:14.160 --> 00:37:16.160
They don't want to listen about it,

00:37:16.360 --> 00:37:19.920
the whole rigmarole of the whole movement of the brain.

00:37:34.000 --> 00:37:37.160
And some of them who try, you see, a little westernized,

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:40.640
they try, you see; they develop an inferiority complex,

00:37:48.920 --> 00:37:51.120
and they go to the left side.

00:38:02.480 --> 00:38:05.800
But there is no need to understand it with mental,

00:38:06.000 --> 00:38:10.520
I mean, to all the time analyzing through your mental process,

00:38:10.720 --> 00:38:13.040
and then to understand everything,

00:38:13.240 --> 00:38:18.320
and then become Sahaja yogis with the heart open.

00:38:18.520 --> 00:38:20.480
This is rather very circuitous.

00:38:20.680 --> 00:38:22.440
But what to do? They have gone that way,

00:38:22.640 --> 00:38:25.400
so they have to come that way.

00:39:07.200 --> 00:39:10.240
Because even if they become Sahaja yogis,

00:39:10.440 --> 00:39:13.520
they start questioning and thinking about it,

00:39:13.720 --> 00:39:16.360
and worrying about it.

00:39:30.960 --> 00:39:34.480
So the false people just mesmerize them

00:39:34.680 --> 00:39:37.640
and take advantage of that mesmerism.

00:40:06.960 --> 00:40:10.760
So one should not feel bad.

00:40:10.960 --> 00:40:15.200
If you feel like analyzing, you should go ahead with it,

00:40:15.400 --> 00:40:19.240
because I cannot stop your speed,

00:40:19.440 --> 00:40:22.120
I'm not going to mesmerize you.

00:40:50.160 --> 00:40:54.760
In Sahaja Yoga the freedom is to be respected.

00:41:03.720 --> 00:41:07.600
But we do not allow people to come for puja

00:41:07.800 --> 00:41:10.720
who have not achieved a certain amount

00:41:10.920 --> 00:41:16.600
of understanding mentally of Sahaja Yoga

00:41:16.800 --> 00:41:18.960
- from the Western people, not in India,

00:41:19.160 --> 00:41:21.760
but here there is a restriction.

00:41:57.280 --> 00:42:03.040
Because supposing in India I do not explain to them,

00:42:03.240 --> 00:42:04.520
they don't want to know.

00:42:04.720 --> 00:42:07.720
They know that they'll get vibrations.

00:42:19.920 --> 00:42:21.560
They already know about vibrations,

00:42:21.760 --> 00:42:24.640
so I don't have to tell them "You will get more vibrations."

00:42:24.840 --> 00:42:27.360
If they get more vibrations they know I am the Shakti,

00:42:27.560 --> 00:42:30.560
that's all, I don't have to explain it.

00:42:40.160 --> 00:42:43.440
Like as you can make out which is the best wine,

00:42:43.640 --> 00:42:46.960
they can make out who is the real person.

00:42:53.920 --> 00:42:56.080
They know the taste of it.

00:43:22.320 --> 00:43:25.720
Now, once in a puja

00:43:25.920 --> 00:43:28.720
I had about six thousand people that touched My Feet.

00:43:28.920 --> 00:43:31.760
So I said, "In a puja now, please don't have

00:43:31.960 --> 00:43:34.760
- the people need not touch My Feet." I said it.

00:43:34.960 --> 00:43:37.600
But they thought it was Dhumal who suggested,

00:43:37.800 --> 00:43:40.480
so they all got after his life.

00:43:40.680 --> 00:43:43.560
They said, "You only want to take all the blessings

00:43:43.760 --> 00:43:46.120
from Mother's Feet, and you didn't want us to take it",

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:48.600
and they got after him.

00:44:23.560 --> 00:44:26.040
Another thing is, you see, in the West

00:44:26.240 --> 00:44:30.760
I never used to make the panchamruta with My Feet but with My Hands,

00:44:30.960 --> 00:44:33.520
because here people would think that

00:44:33.720 --> 00:44:35.520
that's a dirty thing feet is,

00:44:35.720 --> 00:44:37.960
and we should not have of the feet, you see.

00:44:38.160 --> 00:44:40.360
But actually the Feet are very powerful,

00:44:40.600 --> 00:44:43.400
and they can never be dirty.

00:45:30.400 --> 00:45:32.720
Like the River Ganges has vibrations.

00:45:32.920 --> 00:45:34.520
If you have the water of Ganges

00:45:34.720 --> 00:45:37.440
you will see that it will never be dirtied.

00:45:37.640 --> 00:45:40.360
On the contrary, whatever are inside that

00:45:40.560 --> 00:45:42.800
because it's never sort of very kept clean,

00:45:43.000 --> 00:45:45.720
whatever dirt has gone into it,

00:45:45.920 --> 00:45:48.520
it settles down and doesn't dirty the thing at all.

00:45:48.720 --> 00:45:52.560
It's very clean water, all the time vibrating.

00:46:22.560 --> 00:46:26.840
So one must understand whatever is pure,

00:46:27.040 --> 00:46:29.600
which is responsible for purity,

