00:49:55.600 --> 00:50:00.280
Now Ganesha's color is red or orangish.

00:50:00.480 --> 00:50:04.120
Because the child, when it is conceived as a fetus,

00:50:04.320 --> 00:50:07.240
the first color it sees is orange

00:50:07.440 --> 00:50:12.640
of the red wall of the mother's womb, of the blood.

00:50:38.680 --> 00:50:41.520
In Sahaja Yoga, now you must have learnt

00:50:41.720 --> 00:50:47.120
that every action has a reaction, which acts.

00:51:03.800 --> 00:51:08.800
The color of the original,

00:51:09.200 --> 00:51:12.960
we can say the primordial

00:51:13.880 --> 00:51:18.560
Ganesha is just of the clay,

00:51:18.760 --> 00:51:24.480
because He is made out of Mother Earth.

00:51:42.800 --> 00:51:47.280
Now when the Gauri, the Mother of Ganesha created Him

00:51:47.480 --> 00:51:51.840
to protect Her chastity while She was having Her bath,

00:51:52.040 --> 00:51:55.320
She colored Him red, because everybody could see that

00:51:55.520 --> 00:51:59.240
there's somebody sitting there to protect Her.

00:52:23.960 --> 00:52:28.320
So when you see the red color around you as a fetus,

00:52:28.520 --> 00:52:30.320
then you absorb that color,

00:52:30.520 --> 00:52:34.560
and your Ganesha gets colored

00:52:34.760 --> 00:52:37.520
with the red in the same beautiful manner.

00:52:37.720 --> 00:52:41.880
Just it has a reaction of that getting red and it acts,

00:52:42.120 --> 00:52:43.760
means red color of a Ganesha,

00:52:43.960 --> 00:52:49.320
the one who has a red color of a Ganesha, frightens others.

00:52:49.520 --> 00:52:51.320
They know there is Ganesha sitting there,

00:52:51.520 --> 00:52:53.360
a pure, chaste,  personality

00:52:53.560 --> 00:52:57.400
with all the fieriness of the Ganesha is there.

00:53:53.480 --> 00:53:57.480
Now this Ganesha when He is in a childhood,

00:53:57.680 --> 00:54:00.960
as you see, when the child is born,

00:54:01.160 --> 00:54:04.520
the children are extremely

00:54:04.720 --> 00:54:07.560
protective or fiery, you can say,

00:54:07.760 --> 00:54:12.880
about anybody touching their innocence.

00:54:39.320 --> 00:54:43.360
