00:54:46.240 --> 00:54:48.800
they become very aware and they don't like

00:54:49.000 --> 00:54:51.640
their clothes to be taken out in the presence of others.

00:54:51.840 --> 00:54:57.480
They become very shy of their innocence.

00:54:58.320 --> 00:55:00.720
I mean, not shy, shyness is not -

00:55:00.920 --> 00:55:03.640
in the sense of their nudity, very shy of their nudity,

00:55:03.840 --> 00:55:07.160
so that their innocence should not be attacked.

00:55:49.200 --> 00:55:52.040
If their innocence is not attacked and if they are pure,

00:55:52.240 --> 00:55:54.720
if they see a nude woman they'll close their eyes.

