01:17:33.840 --> 01:17:35.960
But fun is a treasure.

01:17:36.160 --> 01:17:39.840
Anything that is full of fun you remember all your life,

01:17:40.040 --> 01:17:45.200
you can tell others, it's such an embodiment of fun-creation.

