01:32:55.240 --> 01:32:58.880
- and suddenly she sees her husband walking in the room!

01:33:34.760 --> 01:33:38.720
But this only He does to the people who are innocent.

01:33:53.200 --> 01:33:56.120
But to the cunning, He punishes.

01:34:02.840 --> 01:34:05.240
He'll go on pouring all kinds of miseries,

01:34:05.440 --> 01:34:06.920
one more than the other, and He'll say,

01:34:07.120 --> 01:34:09.600
"Now cry more, and cry more. You want to cry?

01:34:09.800 --> 01:34:12.720
All right, have it more, and have it more."

01:34:35.960 --> 01:34:38.200
And Hanumana on His side -  say for example,

01:34:38.400 --> 01:34:42.760
when Lakshmana was sick and He had to get some medicine

01:34:42.960 --> 01:34:47.000
from one big mountain,

01:34:48.320 --> 01:34:50.720
He brought the whole mountain, you see.

01:34:51.400 --> 01:34:53.560
Because He said, "I had no time to find it, you see,

01:34:53.760 --> 01:34:56.680
so better find it now," and brought the whole mountain.

01:35:56.560 --> 01:35:58.440
He too is the same style,

01:35:58.640 --> 01:36:02.640
can be very destructive

01:36:02.840 --> 01:36:05.720
when it comes to egoistical people,

01:36:06.120 --> 01:36:09.160
like Ravana - whole Lanka he burnt.

01:36:44.960 --> 01:36:50.320
If Ganesha is painted red, He is painted orange.

01:37:02.520 --> 01:37:06.320
And as Ganesha has to settle down permanently in one place,

01:37:06.520 --> 01:37:11.360
He uses Saint Michael to run up and down the left side.

01:37:11.560 --> 01:37:13.960
While Hanumana can run up and down,

01:37:14.160 --> 01:37:16.960
He need not settle down at a place.

01:37:57.840 --> 01:38:02.120
But though He is a settled Deity, Sthita,

01:38:02.320 --> 01:38:04.240
is the one who is to be settled

01:38:04.440 --> 01:38:07.600
- once He's settled, then He emits vibrations

01:38:07.800 --> 01:38:10.920
which go everywhere.

01:38:28.880 --> 01:38:31.320
He is the source of innocence.

01:38:35.520 --> 01:38:38.520
He is the source of the vibrations.

01:38:43.040 --> 01:38:45.120
He is everything, in a way.

01:38:50.280 --> 01:38:54.360
When He ascends here as Mahaganesha within you,

01:38:54.560 --> 01:38:58.240
and in God He descends as Ganesha

01:38:59.280 --> 01:39:01.560
- from here, on the back.

01:39:53.480 --> 01:39:57.240
So when you think too much about sex,

01:39:58.320 --> 01:40:03.640
your eyes get ruined, because you are using Mahaganesha.

01:40:13.560 --> 01:40:15.720
Your Mahaganesha is spoilt,

01:40:18.520 --> 01:40:20.880
and your eyes starts wobbling.

01:40:46.800 --> 01:40:49.960
The eyes lose innocence, purity,

01:40:56.600 --> 01:41:00.840
and they start absorbing all that is filth.

01:41:10.640 --> 01:41:14.880
The eyes which are pure and innocent

01:41:15.520 --> 01:41:18.080
give innocence to others.

01:41:29.200 --> 01:41:34.080
Not only that, but they are the eyes,

01:41:34.320 --> 01:41:39.120
are the eyes through which the spirit looks out.

01:41:57.920 --> 01:42:01.120
It has many combinations which I have no time to tell you,

01:42:01.320 --> 01:42:03.440
but it's a very bad thing

01:42:03.640 --> 01:42:06.600
that people get those unclean eyes, the bhootish eyes.

01:42:06.800 --> 01:42:09.040
And anybody who is bhootish around

01:42:09.280 --> 01:42:11.360
will turn their eyes to that person,

01:42:11.560 --> 01:42:14.200
because it's a play of the satanic now playing now,

01:42:14.400 --> 01:42:16.120
the negative.

01:43:00.480 --> 01:43:02.840
And that is what we do when

01:43:03.040 --> 01:43:06.680
we do not place Ganesha at right places.

01:43:19.040 --> 01:43:21.840
If we have to make Ganesha reflected

01:43:22.040 --> 01:43:25.400
in our Mahaganesha stage at this point,

01:43:25.600 --> 01:43:29.080
we should try to keep our eyes very clean,

01:43:53.880 --> 01:43:58.280
so that you keep the seat of Mahaganesha clean.

01:44:13.000 --> 01:44:14.440
In the Puja of Shri Ganesh

01:44:14.640 --> 01:44:18.200
you must bring the soft grass also,

01:44:18.400 --> 01:44:21.640
because durva, He's fond of Durva,

01:44:21.840 --> 01:44:25.840
durva, that's called as durva- because the soft grass

01:44:26.040 --> 01:44:29.680
is soothing to the eyes.

01:44:29.880 --> 01:44:35.480
Not only that, but it gives you the green part

01:44:35.680 --> 01:44:38.080
of the Swadisthana Chakra.

01:44:38.280 --> 01:44:43.920
Which -  he exists when we have not started about thinking,

01:44:44.600 --> 01:44:47.400
you have not started the thinking process.

01:44:47.680 --> 01:44:50.400
That suggests that part of Swadisthana,

01:44:50.600 --> 01:44:52.640
when you are not thinking,

01:44:52.840 --> 01:44:57.520
the green part of it, the lower part of the Swadisthana is green.

01:45:44.040 --> 01:45:46.280
So the green is the one:

01:45:46.480 --> 01:45:49.280
at that stage we have not become human beings,

01:45:49.480 --> 01:45:52.760
at that stage it represents the green of Swadisthana,

01:45:52.960 --> 01:45:55.280
where it created the whole universe, everything.

01:45:55.480 --> 01:45:56.920
Up to that it's green.

01:45:57.120 --> 01:45:59.240
Then when it starts creating the ego

01:45:59.440 --> 01:46:02.880
it becomes the yellow color, where it uses the sun,

01:46:03.080 --> 01:46:05.360
the action part.

01:46:10.760 --> 01:46:14.120
Not "uses" the sun but becomes active,

01:46:14.320 --> 01:46:16.440
representing the sun side.

01:46:55.920 --> 01:47:01.440
So the green represents actually the part of

01:47:01.640 --> 01:47:03.760
Ganesha, part of Ganesha in a way,

01:47:03.960 --> 01:47:08.240
because till then you are not thinking.

01:47:08.440 --> 01:47:09.560
You are at a level

01:47:09.760 --> 01:47:12.040
where you are close to the Mother Earth, you see.

01:47:12.240 --> 01:47:14.120
So the Mother Earth is giving, you see.

01:47:14.320 --> 01:47:17.640
The sun part has not started when the green is there,

01:47:17.840 --> 01:47:19.960
because the Mother Earth gives this green.

01:47:20.160 --> 01:47:22.840
Of course the sun makes it green, that's different point,

01:47:23.040 --> 01:47:25.200
but that you don't start doing it.

01:47:25.400 --> 01:47:28.760
When you start doing something yourself at a human level,

01:47:28.960 --> 01:47:30.920
the whole thing becomes yellow.

01:47:31.120 --> 01:47:32.760
So Swadisthana has two sides,

01:47:32.960 --> 01:47:35.080
the physical and the mental side.

01:47:35.280 --> 01:47:36.960
The physical side is the green side,

01:47:37.160 --> 01:47:40.720
and the mental side is the yellow side.

01:49:02.760 --> 01:49:07.640
So now we are today here to worship Shri Ganesh.

01:49:08.120 --> 01:49:12.720
Now I would like you to get some grass from the yard

01:49:13.040 --> 01:49:16.280
some soft grass, because that's an important part of it.

01:49:24.200 --> 01:49:27.880
So you should put your eyes onto the greenery

01:49:28.080 --> 01:49:32.400
to improve your Ganesha.

01:49:57.640 --> 01:49:59.360
And when  it is very warm,

01:49:59.560 --> 01:50:03.160
then you can also walk barefoot on the green

01:50:03.360 --> 01:50:06.520
in the morning-time, when the dew is on it.

01:50:32.480 --> 01:50:35.040
Those who are very overactive

01:50:35.240 --> 01:50:37.160
should take to the vegetarian diet,

01:50:37.360 --> 01:50:42.960
it will help them to become more towards the balanced side.

01:50:43.280 --> 01:50:47.120
Not as a fanaticism, but more on vegetables,

01:50:47.320 --> 01:50:50.520
and eat animals which are very small ones,

01:50:50.720 --> 01:50:52.520
so it's all right.
